title: Matera Storage Bench
description:
The Matera Collection (2007), focused on delivering ample storage, is the work of Sean Yoo, who at the time of its conception lived in Matera, Italy. The Matera Storage Bench features clean lines nicely finished with beveled edges, running match-wood grain, and exposed-slot mortise-and-tenon corner joints, plus a sled base that lends an airy feel. It offers extra room for clothing, bedding and more, with a hinged top for convenient access. Made in Malaysia.
  • Sleek storage solution.
  • Solid wood frame secured with mortise-and-tenon corner joints.
  • Hinged top lifts up to reveal roomy storage space inside.

Design Within Reach

title: Line Storage Bench
description:
A customer favorite since its debut, the Line Collection features geometric frames made out of precisely crafted oak or walnut. It's distinguished by its strong horizontal lines that reflect natural landscapes and lend a sense of restfulness and calm. The Line Storage Bench (2019) features a lift-up top with convenient lid-stay hardware, providing room for storing extra linens, clothes, and more. Made in Malaysia.

title: Gridy Fungi Shelf
description:
Beautiful shelves inspired by one of nature's more whimsical features; the shelf fungus that grows horizontally out of trees in the woods. Use the Gridy Fungi Shelf beside the bed, as a decorative element in the living room, to display colorful spices in the kitchen, or as a landing pad for keys by the front door. Made in Vietnam.
  • Two metal keyholes on the wall-facing surface for easy installation.

title: Corniche Shelving
description:
Brothers Ronan and Erwan Bouroullec are dedicated to the organization of interior spaces. Their wall-mounted Corniches (2012) create small, unobtrusive, accessible storage spaces for all kinds of practical and ornamental objects. Whether used as a place to store car keys beside the front door, a spot for a soap dispenser in the bathroom, or a shelf for a favorite photo, Corniches offer a new way to use the walls in your living space. Made in Italy.
  • Small and unobtrusive.
  • Easily accessible.
  • Practical.
